'''MSE-6-E629L''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[MSE-series|mouse droid]] remotely operated by [[Tonin]], an [[R2-series astromech droid/Legends|R2 unit]]. It could use a special interface installed by Tonin to assume the identity of [[MSE-6-P303K]] while that droid sabotaged [[Iron Fist (Executor-class)|''Iron Fist'']]. This subterfuge kept the [[Super Star Destroyer/Legends|SSD's]] central computer from noticing the absence of much of the ship's utility droid population.

